Reference-contexts: The microcode of the T800 FPU was documented in a restricted subset of occam. Using the occam transformation system developed in Oxford <ref> [2] </ref>, David Shepherd demonstrated that this code was equivalent to a more naturally expressed occam program which had been shown to meet the Z specification.
