Reference-contexts: The transformation system builds on the simple semantics of occam, as expressed by Bill Roscoe and Tony Hoare in <ref> [3] </ref>, allowing essentially mechanical proof that two programs like the specification of the FPU and the implementing microcode have the same effect. There is a very readable non-technical summary of this work in an article in New Scientist [4].
